# Intuition
To determine if the letters are in order, it's enough to compare their ASCII values. We know that if previous letter is less than current letter, letters are in order. This is simplified even more since we know all items will be from lowercase english alphabet.

In javascript, it's not necessary to extract that value using any methods, we can directly compare the strings. 

