1. Convert BST to a sorted array using Inorder traversal
2. Build the balanced BST from sorted array.
    - Recursively choose the middle element of the sorted array as the root of the balanced BST
    - All the elements on the left of the middle element will be part of left subtree and elements on the right of the middle element will be part of right subtree

